The Red Connection 

A free for download Singapore produced Not-For-Profit Evangelistic Telemovie. Created by G&amp;J Creation, Reeds Media and Luwei Performing Arts Fellowship.

A minute in time separated two brothers. Now many years later, the hunger for drugs destroys the life of the brother who stayed with his mother. Only the thread of blood ties can lead the drug addicted brother away from life's worst.

This torrent contains the full DVD of The Red Connection movie. The movie is spoken in Chinese but has both Chinese and English subtitles. 

